# Rebranding to "Charmed" and Rule Enforcement

This plan outlines the steps to rebrand the project from "Alarmify/CharmAlarm" to "Charmed" and ensures all user rules (Pedagogical Protocol, Devil's Advocate, Security, etc.) are strictly followed and enforced.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Data Migration**: Changing the configuration directory from `~/.alarmify` to `~/.charmed` will cause users to lose their settings/alarms unless we migrate them. I will implement a migration step or keep the old path if preferred. For this plan, I assume a full rebrand including the data directory.
> **Environment Variables**: I will rename `ALARMIFY_TEST_MODE` to `CHARMED_TEST_MODE`.

