## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `bandit -r . -ll` to ensure no security regressions.
- Run `pytest tests/` to verify that rebranding didn't break core logic (especially paths and state management).
    ```bash
    .venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/ -v
    ```

### Manual Verification
- Launch the application and verify "Charmed" is displayed in the window title and logo.
- Verify that a new `.charmed` directory is created in the home folder if it doesn't exist.
- Verify that the help/about dialogs (if any) show the new name.
